<i>adverb</i>: 하마터면 [하마터면], 거의 [거의/거이], 가까이 [가까이] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>하마터면 [하마터면]</dt><br>
<dd>almost; barely; nearly</dd><br>
<dd>조금만 잘못했더라면.</dd><br>
<dd>If something had gone wrong even slightly.</dd><br>
<dt>거의 [거의/거이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. all but</dd><br>
<dd>전부에서 조금 모자라게.</dd><br>
<dd>A little less than all.</dd><br>
<dd>2. nearly; almost</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 상태나 한도에 매우 가깝게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being very close to a state or limit.</dd><br>
<dt>가까이 [가까이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. closely</dd><br>
<dd>거리가 멀지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>Not far.</dd><br>
<dd>2. nearly</dd><br>
<dd>어떠한 기준에 거의 다다르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Almost reaching a standard.</dd><br>
<dd>3. closely</dd><br>
<dd>서로 친하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Intimately.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>